item.title: Eye Bento Bouncy Eyeshadow Trio
item.dc:creator: Tinh Le
item.description: 01 Apricot Soda CALCIUM TITANIUM BOROSILICATE, BIS-DIGLYCERYL POLYACYLADIPATE-2, TITANIUM DIOXIDE (CI 77891), CALCIUM SODIUM BOROSILICATE, POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE, SYNTHETIC FLUORPHLOGOPITE, MICA (CI 77019), METHYLPROPANEDIOL, PROPANEDIOL, IRON OXIDES (CI 77491), TIN OXIDE, TRIETHOXYCAPRYLYLSILANE, IRON OXIDES (CI 77499), AQUA/WATER/EAU
item.content:encoded:
What it is: A stacked, creamy, powder eyeshadow in curated trios of shimmers or combinations of matte and shimmer shades.

Ingredient Callouts: Free of sulfates SLS and SLES, parabens, and phthalates. Kaja is cruelty-free.

What Else You Need to Know:These bouncy eyeshadows come packaged in bite-sized shimmer stacks or trios of matte and shimmer pigments that apply effortlessly with your fingertips. Kaja’s Glitter Arrangement Technology delivers uniform shimmer in every swipe—perfect for quick, easy eye looks on-the-go.
